					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The VRC7 <strong>is</strong> a YM2413, except it has the rhythm channels removed (and a few other bits as well) - all you need to do is compare their I/O register layouts and it's easy to see.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
